quest.name: The Most Succulent of Succulents
journal:
î‚¾ Quest Sync
Bhil Bil is looking for an unsuspecting laborer to help him make a quick gil.
objectives: Survey the designated location and slay gigantenders for their flesh.
Deliver a chunk of fruiting gigantender flesh to Bhil Bil.

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Sinner! Over here! You have seen fruiting gigantenders nearby, yes?

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Very aggressive, they are. We Mord stay away from them, but someone like you... Yes, I have an idea.

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: You are healthy, strong! I have a favor to ask. Bring me chunks, big chunks of their flesh.

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Go east from here and you will find them, or they will find you! You shall be rewarded if you do as I say. Quickly, now!

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Still here, but why? Maybe you have changed your mind, yes?

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: You have it? Show me, show me!

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: You have done well. Very well...

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Heh heh... This is not for Mord mouths, no. A fine price this will fetch, though.

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Sinners like you enjoy the flesh of the little ones. The big ones, not so much.

dialogue.name: BHILBIL
dialogue.text: Yes, little ones are good for selling, but hard to catch, hard to kill. But not so difficult for you, it seems...
